Interface MultiQuantifierEliminator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIterativeMultiQuantifierEliminator, AbstractMultiQuantifierEliminator, AbstractSGVET, BruteForceMultiQuantifierEliminator, DefaultMultiQuantifierEliminator, SamplingIfNeededMultiQuantifierEliminator, SamplingSingleQuantifierEliminator, SGVET

    public interface MultiQuantifierEliminator
    Interface to classes able to eliminate quantification (for a fixed group) over given indices, constraint and body.

    braz
